{"tid":2019373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［擠牙膏］《外交》：中國軍方既武漢肺炎資料庫流出 涉及230城市 可為中國既誠信‘提供insight’","createTime":"2020-05-16T08:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T11:36:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e51a4fdc614467e2463884d51122ea87e330093f","tid":2019373,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYbHpfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYbHpfc.png&h=9ea7128b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯  A dataset of coronavirus cases and deaths from the military&rsquo;s National University of Defense Technology, leaked to Foreign Policy, offers insight into how Beijing has gathered coronavirus data on its population. <br />\n<br />\nThe source of the leak, who asked to remain anonymous because of the sensitivity of sharing Chinese military data, said that the data came from the university. The school publishes a data tracker for the coronavirus: The online version matches with the leaked information, except it is far less detailed&mdash;it shows just the map of cases, not the distinct data.⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/05/12/leaked-chinese-coronavirus-database-number-cases/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2Fleaked-chinese-coronavirus-database-number-cases%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=fa755744\" target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/05/12/leaked-chinese-coronavirus-database-number-cases/</a>"},{"pid":"4a7e3696de7fc84e7d966ff14b9261b5e25f263d","tid":2019373,"uid":324084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"竟然唔過100萬"},{"pid":"4e6a7db0f57bf0cf38af193c017392e3ef5dae8c","tid":2019373,"uid":182875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a7e3696de7fc84e7d966ff14b9261b5e25f263d","tid":2019373,"uid":324084,"like":1